r joining me on this tour of A Family-Friendly Theme Park Resort! I hope you've enjoyed this glimpse into the heart of our magical world. Feel free to explore these wonderful landmarks and create your own unforgettable adventures. Enjoy the rest of your day!", "labels": [{"number": 1, "location_name": "Grand Entrance Pavilion", "ymin": 156.0, "xmin": 0.0, "ymax": 500.0, "xmax": 490.0, "semantic_reason": "The large grey building structure with multiple roofs and an arched entrance, designated as the main entrance."}, {"number": 2, "location_name": "Splashworks Lagoon", "ymin": 512.0, "xmin": 181.0, "ymax": 594.0, "xmax": 299.0, "semantic_reason": "The distinct blue, oval-shaped water body located to the right of the Grand Entrance Pavilion."}, {"number": 3, "location_name": "Festival Promenade", "ymin": 600.0, "xmin": 480.0, "ymax": 900.0, "xmax": 995.0, "semantic_reason": "The large, circular paved area forming the base upon which the golden spire sits."}, {"number": 4, "location_name": "Adventure Central Spire", "ymin": 106.0, "xmin": 501.0, "ymax": 810.0, "xmax": 994.0, "semantic_reason": "The prominent golden, ornate, spire-like structure rising from the circular paved base."}, {"number": 5, "location_name": "Discovery Gardens", "ymin": 0.0, "xmin": 700.0, "ymax": 320.0, "xmax": 999.0, "semantic_reason": "A distinct cluster of green trees and ground cover located in the top-right quadrant of the map."}]}
