INFO:tools.adk_tools:Content of vision_proposal: {"script": "Welcome, adventurers, to the magnificent A Family-Friendly Theme Park Resort! I'm absolutely thrilled to be your guide today as we embark on a truly enchanting journey through some of our most beloved and iconic landmarks. Get ready to explore, imagine, and make wonderful memories! Our grand adventure begins right here, at the impressive Grand Entrance Pavilion. Just look at this architectural masterpiece! Its stately grey stone, soaring rooftops, and intricate details truly set the stage for the magic that awaits inside. Imagine the excitement of guests as they step through these magnificent arches, eager to begin their day of fun and discovery. This isn't just an entrance; it's a gateway to an unforgettable world, designed to inspire awe and wonder from the very first moment. Notice the elegant dormers peeking from the slate roofs and the grand windows that invite light into its expansive halls. It’s truly a symbol of the resort’s commitment to beauty and welcoming hospitality. Now, as we stroll clockwise from our starting point, just a short distance to our right, you'll discover the sparkling turquoise waters of the Splashworks Lagoon. Isn't it inviting? This serene oasis is a perfect spot for families to cool off and play. Imagine the joyous splashes and laughter echoing from this vibrant pool area on a warm day. It's a delightful haven for aquatic fun, offering a refreshing escape and endless entertainment for all ages. The lagoon’s gentle curves and vibrant blue hues make it a picturesque stop, hinting at the fun-filled aquatic adventures that are a signature part of our resort experience. It’s a wonderful blend of relaxation and exhilaration, designed for everyone to enjoy. Continuing our delightful journey, we now find ourselves in the heart of the resort’s vibrant energy, the spectacular Festival Promenade. This sprawling, paved area forms a grand circle, offering panoramic views and serving as a central gathering point for all our guests. Feel the excitement in the air! This is where parades often begin, where impromptu street performances might surprise you, and where the resort’s lively atmosphere truly comes alive. It’s designed not just for walking, but for celebrating, connecting, and soaking in the festive spirit that defines our park. Look around you; this spacious plaza connects many of our key attractions, making it a bustling hub of activity and a perfect place to pause and take it all in. And what better to marvel at from the Festival Promenade than the breathtaking Adventure Central Spire! Just look up at its gleaming golden glory, reaching majestically towards the sky. This incredible, ornate spire is truly a beacon of adventure, adorned with intricate carvings and symbols that tell tales of daring quests and heroic journeys. It stands as a testament to the spirit of exploration and discovery that permeates our entire resort. Whether it's catching the morning sun or sparkling under the moonlight, the Adventure Central Spire is an unforgettable landmark, guiding adventurers both young and old through our magical realm. Its intricate details invite closer inspection, revealing stories hidden within its golden facade. Finally, to complete our wonderful clockwise circuit, we'll gently wander into the tranquil beauty of the Discovery Gardens. Tucked away in this peaceful corner, these lush green spaces offer a serene contrast to the bustling promenade. Here, vibrant flora, towering trees, and meandering paths invite you to slow down, breathe deeply, and reconnect with nature. It’s a place for quiet contemplation, a lovely picnic, or simply enjoying the natural beauty. The meticulously cared-for foliage provides a calming atmosphere, perfect for a peaceful interlude before you dive back into the excitement of the park. It's a natural masterpiece, a living canvas that changes with the seasons, offering a different charm with every visit. Thank you for joining me on this tour of A Family-Friendly Theme Park Resort! I hope you've enjoyed this glimpse into the heart of our magical world. Feel free to explore these wonderful landmarks and create your own unforgettable adventures. Enjoy the rest of your day!", "labels": [{"number": 1, "location_name": "Grand Entrance Pavilion", "ymin": 156.0, "xmin": 80.0, "ymax": 500.0, "xmax": 570.0, "semantic_reason": "The large grey building structure with multiple roofs and an arched entrance, designated as the main entrance."}, {"number": 2, "location_name": "Splashworks Lagoon", "ymin": 512.0, "xmin": 181.0, "ymax": 594.0, "xmax": 299.0, "semantic_reason": "The distinct blue, oval-shaped water body located to the right of the Grand Entrance Pavilion."}, {"number": 3, "location_name": "Festival Promenade", "ymin": 600.0, "xmin": 405.0, "ymax": 900.0, "xmax": 920.0, "semantic_reason": "The large, circular paved area forming the base upon which the golden spire sits."}, {"number": 4, "location_name": "Adventure Central Spire", "ymin": 106.0, "xmin": 427.0, "ymax": 810.0, "xmax": 920.0, "semantic_reason": "The prominent golden, ornate, spire-like structure rising from the circular paved base."}, {"number": 5, "location_name": "Discovery Gardens", "ymin": 0.0, "xmin": 621.0, "ymax": 320.0, "xmax": 920.0, "semantic_reason": "A distinct cluster of green trees and ground cover located in the top-right quadrant of the map."}]}
