onvenience of the Visitor Center. It’s a place for reflection, for sharing your newfound discoveries with friends and family, or simply taking a moment to appreciate the tranquility before heading home. Thank you so much for joining me on this tour of A Local Nature Park and Wildlife Reserve. I hope you've enjoyed your visit as much as I've enjoyed guiding you through these incredible spaces!", 'labels': [{'number': 1, 'location_name': 'Park Visitor Center', 'ymin': 110.0, 'xmin': 185.0, 'ymax': 425.0, 'xmax': 625.0, 'x': 405.0, 'y': 267.5, 'bbox_type': 'landmark', 'semantic_reason': 'The large grey building at the top of the map, clearly identifiable as the main facility with an entrance.', 'anchor_policy': 'center'}, {'number': 2, 'location_name': 'Old Growth Forest', 'ymin': 195.0, 'xmin': 650.0, 'ymax': 335.0, 'xmax': 720.0, 'x': 685.0, 'y': 265.0, 'bbox_type': 'landmark', 'semantic_reason': "A distinct, small rectangular green area to the right of the visitor center, labelled 'Wiliden Horretlen The Corfrn' which implies a cultivated garden or forest section.", 'anchor_policy': 'center'}, {'number': 3, 'location_name': 'Beaver Creek Wetlands', 'ymin': 465.0, 'xmin': 475.0, 'ymax': 855.0, 'xmax': 895.0, 'x': 685.0, 'y': 660.0, 'bbox_type': 'landmark', 'semantic_reason': "The prominent blue water body with islands in the lower-right section, labelled 'Borvian Or sebviar' and connected to 'Beaver Creek Wetlands' text.", 'anchor_policy': 'center'}, {'number': 4, 'location_name': 'Wildlife Observation Platform', 'ymin': 490.0, 'xmin': 185.0, 'ymax': 845.0, 'xmax': 485.0, 'x': 335.0, 'y': 667.5, 'bbox_type': 'landmark', 'semantic_reason': 'The large, distinct hexagonal wooden structure in the lower-left area, visually a platform.', 'anchor_policy': 'center'}, {'number': 5, 'location_name': 'Park Entrance Plaza', 'ymin': 420.0, 'xmin': 295.0, 'ymax': 490.0, 'xmax': 695.0, 'x': 495.0, 'y': 455.0, 'bbox_type': 'landmark', 'semantic_reason': "The wide, paved grey stone area directly in front of the Park Visitor Center's main entrance, serving as a gathering and arrival space.", 'anchor_policy': 'center'}]}
