    "script": "Welcome, adventurers, to the most exhilarating resort experience, where every corner holds a new discovery! I'm absolutely thrilled to be your guide today as we embark on a journey through our magnificent Family-Friendly Theme Park Resort. Get ready to be amazed, delighted, and maybe even a little splashed! Our adventure begins right here, at the heart of our operations, what we proudly call the Visitor Services Center. Just look at this impressive, modern grey building right before us. This isn't just a place for information; it's your first port of call for anything you might need during your stay. Our dedicated team inside is ready to assist with tickets, reservations, special requests, and even help you plan your perfect day. Think of it as your personal concierge hub, ensuring your visit is as smooth and magical as possible. We encourage everyone to pop in, grab a map, and say hello! Now, as we step out from the Visitor Services Center, we find ourselves in a bustling and vibrant space – this is our magnificent Main Gathering Square. Notice the beautiful, expansive stone paving beneath our feet? This open-air plaza acts as the grand foyer to our resort's aquatic wonders and architectural marvels. It’s a fantastic spot to meet up with family and friends, grab a quick snack from one of the nearby carts, or simply take a moment to soak in the lively atmosphere before diving into the excitement. From here, you’ll have clear views of several of our key attractions, setting the stage for what’s to come. Speaking of views, if you look directly to our right, your eyes will undoubtedly be drawn to the shimmering, golden spectacle that is our Central Discovery Dome. Isn't it just breathtaking? This iconic hexagonal structure, with its radiant golden roof, is a beacon of innovation and wonder. Inside, it houses our most immersive and educational exhibits, designed to spark curiosity and inspire discovery in visitors of all ages. It's a place where science, art, and technology converge to create unforgettable learning experiences. The dome itself is a masterpiece of design, reflecting the sun's rays and standing as a true landmark of our resort. We'll be heading there later, but for now, let’s continue our journey. As we move past the Main Gathering Square and the grandeur of the Central Discovery Dome, prepare to be enchanted by the refreshing vista that unfolds before us: the spectacular Geyser Springs! This isn't just any pool; it's a sprawling aquatic playground, a true oasis of fun and relaxation. You can see the vibrant blue waters stretching out, dotted with incredible interactive play structures that promise endless joy for our younger guests and the young-at-heart. Imagine splashing under playful fountains, navigating adventurous water slides, and enjoying the sun's embrace. It's truly a watery wonderland, designed with every family member in mind, offering both thrilling adventures and serene spots to unwind. And while we're enjoying the lively atmosphere of Geyser Springs, cast your gaze to our far left, nestled charmingly within the aquatic landscape, you'll discover the serene beauty of the Nature Walk Gardens. This delightful green oasis, with its lush foliage and vibrant plant life, provides a peaceful counterpoint to the energetic splashes of the water park. It's a meticulously crafted area where you can take a tranquil stroll, appreciate the botanical diversity, and perhaps even find a quiet bench for a moment of reflection. The gardens are designed to offer a refreshing break, a little slice of natural tranquility right within our bustling resort. They showcase our commitment to integrating natural beauty with thrilling entertainment. And there you have it, a glimpse into just five of the incredible highlights that make our resort truly special. From the welcoming embrace of the Visitor Services Center to the educational wonders of the Central Discovery Dome, the playful allure of Geyser Springs, the community spirit of the Main Gathering Square, and the tranquil charm of the Nature Walk Gardens, every element is designed to create unforgettable memories. I hope you're as excited as I am to explore everything else our Family-Friendly Theme Park Resort has to offer. Let the adventure continue!",
    "labels": [
        {
            "number": 1,
            "location_name": "Visitor Services Center",
            "ymin": 80.0,
            "xmin": 80.0,
